strings: <voice_0x010011E6><se_high>My name is Alex, I live in the world for many years. I took this photo with my own hands.
<voice_0x010011E7><se_high>Let me tell you a story. Forgotten moments lost in the vast ocean of history. The origin of magic...
<voice_0x010011E8><se_high>He came from the Cranbartle family. The family is descended from one of the legendary seven sages.
<voice_0x010011E9><se_high>But my generation has seen the wonderful legacy passed down through marriage from the Albert family. Hi, I have been selected to take a place.
<voice_0x010011EA><se_high>The eldest son is always from the Albert family.
<voice_0x010011EB><se_high>But when the life of the last heir, Alistair, ends, a dark and evil force destroys this bond...
<voice_0x010011EC><se_high>However, I am of the Albert family.
<voice_0x010011ED><se_high>So I will do my best to help the Albert family.
<voice_0x010011EE><se_high>I want you to remove the marijuana statues of the Ku Klux Klan. I have no doubt that you will find them useful.
<voice_0x010011EF><se_high>Since then, only Jessica has been able to inherit the Albert family blood. please help him
